items.description:
When a ticket is:
Created
And the following conditions are met:
Queue in list "Support de Niveau I or Support de Niveau II"
Then execute the following actions:
Send notification e-mail ([2025] Confirmation Ticket) to Ticket Contact (sylvie.gouedart@afimes.com); Ticket Creator (sylvie.gouedart@afimes.com)
Initiated by Sylvie GOUEDART
items.title: Workflow Rule "[TICKET] Notification 01 :  Création ticket" fired.

items.description:
When a ticket is:
Time Added By Autotask Resource
And the following conditions are met:
Status in list "In Progress or Waiting Customer or Waiting for Supplier or Waiting for Delivery"
Queue not in list "[ARCHIVÉ] No Notifications or Commercial or Devis"
Then execute the following actions:
Send notification e-mail (2020_Note) to Additional Contact(s); Assigned Resources (matheo.teneur@acitechnology.fr); Ticket Contact (sylvie.gouedart@afimes.com)
Initiated by Mathéo TENEUR
items.title: Workflow Rule "2020_Entrée_de_temps" fired.

Time Added By Autotask Resource
And the following conditions are met:
Status in list "Complete"
Queue not in list "[ARCHIVÉ] No Notifications or Commercial or Devis"
Then execute the following actions:
Send notification e-mail (2020_Ticket_complété) to Assigned Resources (matheo.teneur@acitechnology.fr); Ticket Contact (sylvie.gouedart@afimes.com)
